title: Constraints on Dark Matter Models from Supermassive Black Hole Evolution
summary: This paper uses JWST and pre-JWST observations to constrain dark matter models based on stellar mass-BH mass relations, reproducing high-redshift SMBH data.
usefulness_reason: Score 70 assigned because the paper explicitly refers to "JWST and pre-JWST observations" and "high-redshift SMBH data", which are types of survey data used for analysis.
